title: Near-total internet blackout hits Gaza as Israel ramps up strikes
description: A near-total internet and blackout has taken hold across much of Gaza, according to witnesses there and companies that monitor global connectivity.

title: Duolingo creator to be inducted into Inventors Hall of Fame
description: Luis von Ahn, the man behind Duolingo and Recaptcha, is being inducted into the Inventors Hall of Fame for his contributions to language learning the technological landscape. He sat down with NBC's Emilie Ikeda to discuss the inspiration for his creations.

title: It was youth night at a Maine bowling alley when gunfire erupted
description: Youth league bowlers and deaf corn hole players were among the dead in Lewiston, Maine, where 18 people were killed by a gunman.
